title: Fantasy Week: Sony Michel Traded, RB Breakdown, Thoughts on Cowboys & Saints players (Football 8/26)
description:
Jamey Eisenberg joins Will Brinson for the continuation of Fantasy Week to react to the Patriots trading Sony Michel to the Rams and much more in the fantasy football landscape heading into the 2021 NFL season.

'Pick Six' is available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Stitcher, Google Podcasts, Castbox and wherever else you listen to podcasts.
